  <bodyText><![CDATA[<p><img src="/media/13084132/1113-d81ott97-vastavalo-340196.jpg" alt="Lapland Short Breaks" data-udi="umb://media/38a1fafa02334560965c9f19ed9bf6b5" /></p>
<p> </p>
<p>As well as our <a data-udi="umb://document/fd2e5d7929b4463883ca4109fd714cc4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fd2e5d7929b4463883ca4109fd714cc4}" title="Muotka 7 Night Adventure">Muotka 7 Night Adventure Weeks</a>, there is now the opportunity to visit magical <a data-udi="umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2da7ac9814d44a75af6718b02ca02250}" title="Lapland/Finland">Lapland</a>, in northerly <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselkä</a>, for a short break. Have a weekend away with an activity package included, from a choice of two amazing hotels:</p>
<div class="g6" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Muotka Wilderness Lodge Short Break<a data-udi="umb://document/fd2e5d7929b4463883ca4109fd714cc4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fd2e5d7929b4463883ca4109fd714cc4}" title="Muotka 7 Night Adventure"><br /></a></h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/fd2e5d7929b4463883ca4109fd714cc4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/fd2e5d7929b4463883ca4109fd714cc4}" title="Muotka 7 Night Adventure"><img src="/media/13073431/muotka_panorama_log-cabin_outside-1.jpg" alt="Muotka Wilderness Lodge" data-udi="umb://media/1b60762e6f054fe88b854bbb924d7bc1" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><a data-udi="umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5fff74e4dcc94dfab5862d08d14d26c2}" title="Muotka Wilderness Lodge">Muotka Wilderness Lodge</a> is a lovingly renovated family-run property set in a secluded snow-laden winter wonderland. Its idyllic location, on the edge of the pristine Urho-Kekkonen National Park, guarantees minimal light pollution and therefore an increased potential for seeing the Northern Lights, simply by stepping outside the lodge's front door.</p>
<h3>What's Included</h3>
<ul>
<li>45 minute transfer time</li>
<li>Chose from either a Wilderness Room, Superior Room with Sauna or Panorama Log Cabin</li>
<li>Aurora alert buzzer</li>
<li>Full thermal clothing for excursions</li>
<li>A gentle snowshoeing tour</li>
<li>Cross-country skiing</li>
<li>Aurora hunt by car</li>
<li>Aurora camp by snowmobile pulled sled</li>
</ul>
</div>
<div class="g6" style="border-bottom: 1px solid #dedede;">
<h3 style="text-align: center;">Star Arctic Hotel Short Break<a data-udi="umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77}" title="Star Arctic Hotel"><br /></a></h3>
<p><a data-udi="umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77}" title="Star Arctic Hotel"><img src="/media/13082822/star-arctic-high-39.jpg" alt="The Star Arctic Hotel" data-udi="umb://media/1f1dcdb77c744af0904308772c18e48b" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span><a data-udi="umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6dce0df99b4e4c64ada8985e9a365f77}" title="Star Arctic Hotel">The Star Arctic Hotel</a> is a modern and stylish hotel boasting spacious Lappish-style suites and Aurora cabins.  A great choice for those looking for an intimate and exclusive feel stay, it is </span><span>located at the top of Kaunispaä fell, away from the light pollution of the village centre and a</span><span>n excellent </span><span>spot from which to view the <a data-udi="umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb4bd30fc93b4d8389fe8d36c8a86995}" title="Northern Lights">Northern Lights</a>.</span><br /><a data-udi="umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7d16724b0f3b4033952b780a65425621}?0 style=" title="Muotka 2-Centre Adventure" data-anchor="?0 style="></a></p>
<h3>What's Included</h3>
<ul>
<li>30 minute transfer time</li>
<li>Chose from either a Scenic View Suite or Aurora Glass Cabin</li>
<li>Multi-taster Lapland experience package including snowmobiling, reindeer &amp; husky sledge rides</li>
<li>Private jacuzzi session and massage</li>
<li>A gentle snowshoeing tour</li>
</ul>
</div>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>For winter season 2021/22 the direct flying is not available, but we hope to offer this for winter season 2022/23. Both accommodations are bookable for an amazing 7 night holiday.</strong></p>
<p> </p>
